snippet.title: Yoomp!64
snippet.description:
Yoomp!64 - my game for Commodore C64
The idea of it comes from Atari game "Yoomp!"
Cartridge available here:
https://rgcd.bigcartel.com/product/yoomp-64-commodore-64
Disk version:
http://www.psytronik.net/newsite/index.php/c64/100-yoomp

https://rgcddev.itch.io/yoomp-64
